data.description: Welcome to your ideal single-story haven! This charming residence boasts 3 generous bedrooms and 2 beautifully appointed bathrooms, and it's perfectly situated alongside a serene park. Upon entering, you'll be immediately drawn to the seamless flow of the open-concept living spaces, including a spacious living room, a versatile dining area, and a well-appointed kitchen that's designed for both functionality and style. The master suite provides a peaceful retreat, complete with an ensuite bathroom and ample closet space. Two additional bedrooms offer versatility for accommodating guests, or setting up a home office.  Step outside to your private backyard oasis, where you can enjoy alfresco dining, gardening, or simply unwind while appreciating the scenic views of the park. The proximity to this park is a true treasure, allowing for daily nature walks, picnics, and outdoor adventures right at your doorstep. Easy  access to Downtown, Pearland and the Medical Center
